  <div class="info-section">
    <h2>Who is this app for?</h2>
    <p>This app is designed for individuals who are looking to improve their self-awareness and personal growth through regular reflection and journaling.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section">
    <h2>How to use this app</h2>
    <p>Simply sign up or log in to start creating posts. Each post allows you to reflect on your day, your emotions, and the tasks you completed or plan to complete.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section">
    <h2>Story of the Developer</h2>
    <p>This app was created by a dedicated developer who wanted to provide a tool for people to track their personal growth and mental well-being. Inspired by the principles of Adlerian psychology, this app encourages users to separate their tasks from others' and focus on what they can control.</p>
